    Implementation of ICapabilityContainer with support for delegation to another ICapabilityContainer.

    The delegate is set by calling bindDelegate(ICapabilityContainer) on this object (or by requesting the ICapabilityDelegation capability). The delegate can only be set once. Delegation will also take IExtendedCapabilityContainer into account. IExtendedCapabilityContainer.addCapability(Class, Object) will not be delegated.
